  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1486340/" class="title-link">心灵的光</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1486340"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/xiaohaoshayu/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1986022-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xiaohaoshayu/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">沙欤@小号鲨鱼</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-09-01"
      class="main-meta">2008-09-01 21:27:49</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1486340_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  <p class="main-title-tip">
                    这篇书评可能有关键情节透露
                  </p>
